---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
	title="Sleep Well Sound Lab - Deep Sleep & Focus Soundscapes" 
	description="Quiet is more than the absence of sound; it is the presence of peace. Discover custom-designed acoustic environments engineered to raise the auditory baseline, block distractions, and help overactive minds find deep, restful sleep."
>
	<!-- Hero Section -->
	<section class="channel-hero">
		<div class="hero-glow"></div>
		<div class="container hero-container">
			<span class="badge sleep-badge">Official YouTube Channel</span>
			<h1 class="page-title">Sleep Well <br/><span class="text-gradient">Sound Lab</span></h1>
			<p class="page-lead">
				Quiet is more than the absence of sound; it is the presence of peace. In a world that is always on, finding a way to truly shut down at the end of the day is a universal challenge. Sleep Well Sound Lab offers custom-designed acoustic environments engineered to raise the auditory baseline, block distractions, and help overactive minds find deep, restful sleep.
			</p>
			<div class="cta-actions">
				<a href="https://www.youtube.com/@SleepWellSoundLab?sub_confirmation=1" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-yt-primary">
					<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="btn-yt-icon" fill="currentColor">
						<path d="M23.498 6.163a3.003 3.003 0 0 0-2.11-2.11C19.518 3.5 12 3.5 12 3.5s-7.518 0-9.388.553a3.003 3.003 0 0 0-2.11 2.11C0 8.033 0 12 0 12s0 3.967.502 5.837a3.003 3.003 0 0 0 2.11 2.11c1.87.553 9.388.553 9.388.553s7.518 0 9.388-.553a3.003 3.003 0 0 0 2.11-2.11C24 15.967 24 12 24 12s0-3.967-.502-5.837zM9.545 15.568V8.432L15.818 12l-6.273 3.568z"/>
					</svg>
					Subscribe on YouTube
				</a>
				<a href="/#player" class="btn btn-secondary">Try Sound Generator</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Featured Videos Section -->
	<section class="videos-section">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="section-header text-center">
				<span class="sub-badge">Featured Listening</span>
				<h2>Popular Sound Labs</h2>
				<p>12-hour continuous auditory shields engineered for deep sleep, cortisol reduction, and focus. Black screen with no mid-roll ads.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="grid grid-3-col">
				<!-- Video Card 1 -->
				<div class="glass-card video-card">
					<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SfNwwV6Yf9E" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="video-preview-link">
						<div class="video-preview">
							<div class="video-overlay-glow"></div>
							<div class="play-btn">
								<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="play-icon-svg" fill="currentColor">
									<path d="M8 5v14l11-7z"/>
								</svg>
							</div>
							<span class="duration">12:00:00</span>
						</div>
					</a>
					<div class="video-meta">
						<h4>Subterranean Rainfall</h4>
						<p class="video-desc">Brown & White Noise for Sleep & Focus | Black Screen | No Ads</p>
						<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SfNwwV6Yf9E" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="video-link-btn">Listen on YouTube →</a>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Video Card 2 -->
				<div class="glass-card video-card">
					<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jfzF3eK3q3A" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="video-preview-link">
						<div class="video-preview">
							<div class="video-overlay-glow"></div>
							<div class="play-btn">
								<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="play-icon-svg" fill="currentColor">
									<path d="M8 5v14l11-7z"/>
								</svg>
							</div>
							<span class="duration">12:00:00</span>
						</div>
					</a>
					<div class="video-meta">
						<h4>Coastal Calm</h4>
						<p class="video-desc">Brown & White Noise for Cortisol Reduction | Black Screen | No Ads</p>
						<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jfzF3eK3q3A" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="video-link-btn">Listen on YouTube →</a>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Video Card 3 -->
				<div class="glass-card video-card">
					<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nJE-zI_UUO0" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="video-preview-link">
						<div class="video-preview">
							<div class="video-overlay-glow"></div>
							<div class="play-btn">
								<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="play-icon-svg" fill="currentColor">
									<path d="M8 5v14l11-7z"/>
								</svg>
							</div>
							<span class="duration">12:00:00</span>
						</div>
					</a>
					<div class="video-meta">
						<h4>Wind Tunnel White Noise</h4>
						<p class="video-desc">Sleep & Focus | Black Screen | No Ads</p>
						<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nJE-zI_UUO0" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="video-link-btn">Listen on YouTube →</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	/* Hero Section */
	.channel-hero {
		position: relative;
		padding: 8rem 2rem 5rem 2rem;
		text-align: center;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.hero-glow {
		position: absolute;
		top: -150px;
		left: 50%;
		transform: translateX(-50%);
		width: 900px;
		height: 450px;
		background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(127, 0, 255, 0.18) 0%, rgba(79, 172, 254, 0.08) 50%, transparent 100%);
		filter: blur(80px);
		z-index: 1;
		pointer-events: none;
	}

	.hero-container {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 10;
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.badge {
		background: rgba(127, 0, 255, 0.1);
		border: 1px solid rgba(127, 0, 255, 0.2);
		color: var(--accent-blue);
		padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
		border-radius: 99px;
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		display: inline-block;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.sleep-badge {
		color: #a855f7;
		border-color: rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.3);
		background: rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.08);
	}

	.page-title {
		font-size: 4rem;
		line-height: 1.1;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		letter-spacing: -0.03em;
	}

	.page-lead {
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
		max-width: 650px;
		margin-left: auto;
		margin-right: auto;
	}

	.cta-actions {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1.75rem;
	}

	/* Buttons */
	.btn {
		padding: 0 2rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		font-weight: 600;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		transition: var(--transition-bounce);
		cursor: pointer;
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		gap: 0.75rem;
		line-height: 1.2;
		height: 48px;
	}

	.btn-yt-primary {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff0000 0%, #cc0000 100%);
		color: #fff;
		border: 1px solid transparent;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);
	}

	.btn-yt-primary:hover {
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.4);
	}

	.btn-yt-icon {
		width: 18px;
		height: 18px;
		display: block;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}

	.btn-secondary {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
		color: var(--text-primary);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
	}

	.btn-secondary:hover {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
		transform: translateY(-2px);
	}

	/* Videos Section */
	.videos-section {
		padding: 4rem 0 6rem 0;
	}

	.section-header {
		max-width: 600px;
		margin: 0 auto 4rem auto;
	}

	.section-header h2 {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.sub-badge {
		color: #a855f7;
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
		display: block;
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
	}

	.text-center {
		text-align: center;
	}

	/* Video Cards */
	.video-card {
		padding: 0;
		overflow: hidden;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		height: 100%;
	}

	.video-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-6px);
		border-color: rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.3);
		box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5), 0 0 25px rgba(127, 0, 255, 0.1);
	}

	.video-preview-link {
		display: block;
		text-decoration: none;
		color: inherit;
	}

	.video-preview {
		height: 180px;
		position: relative;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 50%, #172554 100%);
	}

	.video-overlay-glow {
		position: absolute;
		inset: 0;
		background: radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
		opacity: 0.7;
	}

	.play-btn {
		width: 56px;
		height: 56px;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
		border-radius: 50%;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		color: #fff;
		z-index: 10;
		transition: var(--transition-bounce);
		backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
		padding: 12px;
	}

	.play-icon-svg {
		width: 20px;
		height: 20px;
		color: #fff;
		margin-left: 2px; /* visual centering */
	}

	.video-card:hover .play-btn {
		background: #ff0000;
		border-color: #ff0000;
		transform: scale(1.1);
		box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.6);
	}

	.duration {
		position: absolute;
		bottom: 10px;
		right: 10px;
		background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85);
		color: #fff;
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
		border-radius: 4px;
		z-index: 10;
	}

	.video-meta {
		padding: 2rem;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.75rem;
		flex-grow: 1;
	}

	.video-meta h4 {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		color: var(--text-primary);
		line-height: 1.4;
	}

	.video-desc {
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		line-height: 1.5;
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		flex-grow: 1;
	}

	.video-link-btn {
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: #ff3b30;
		margin-top: 0.5rem;
		align-self: flex-start;
		transition: var(--transition-smooth);
	}

	.video-card:hover .video-link-btn {
		color: #ff453a;
		text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(255, 69, 58, 0.4);
	}

	/* Containers & Grids */
	.container {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 2rem;
	}

	.grid {
		display: grid;
		gap: 2.5rem;
	}

	.grid-3-col {
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
	}

	@media (max-width: 900px) {
		.grid-3-col {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.page-title {
			font-size: 3rem;
		}
		
		.page-lead {
			font-size: 1.15rem;
			padding-left: 1rem;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 480px) {
		.cta-actions {
			flex-direction: column;
			gap: 1rem;
		}
		.btn {
			width: 100%;
			justify-content: center;
		}
	}
</style>
